data.description: Come and see this beautiful home located on a corner lot near Goodfellow AFB! Nicely remodeled 3 bedroom 2 bath home with open concept. Kitchen has been expanded with all new cabinets, countertops and new electric oven and microwave. The dining room is perfect for those holiday dinners and entertaining. New central heating and air unit! Fresh paint and new flooring. Both bathrooms have been charmingly remodeled. New roof and move in ready!
